reviewText: My husband is a big fan of Alonzo Bodden so I got this DVD for him and we both enjoyed it.
Title: Alonzo Bodden - Tall, Dark, and Funny

reviewText: I recently saw Alonzo Bodden on The Tonight Show, and thought he was really funny, so looked him up on Amazon.com and ordered this dvd, which was mentioned on the Tonight Show as just having been released.  I highly recommend this DVD, "Tall, Dark and Funny" to Everyone, no matter what your ethnic background. He is not overly fouled mouthed, which personally, I like. I don't think anyone will be disappointed with "Tall, Dark & Funny," which Alonzo Bodden definitely is!
summary: Alonzo Bodden is a Definite Winner with This Performance!
Title: Alonzo Bodden - Tall, Dark, and Funny

reviewText: Alonzo Bodden is a funny, funny man! This is a great DVD that showcases some of his best bitts on stage.
Title: Alonzo Bodden - Tall, Dark, and Funny

reviewText: I did not enjoy this dvd with Alonzo Bodden as much as I loved his other Album called "No one is listening"-something like that. He is a very very funny man. My wife and I love listening to him on the radio and enjoyed the dvd I listed.
Title: Alonzo Bodden - Tall, Dark, and Funny

reviewText: I like Alonzo and think he is witty and funny; however, this DVD just didn't bring out the funny material I'm used to hearing.  I laughed at his clips on youtube...I didn't laugh once while watching this DVD.  Save your money and just watch his clips on youtube.
